race.comment: CANTILEVER (1) is knocking on the door this campaign, finishing off well over the mile last start before being claimed late in the race. Back to 1400m today doesn't look an issue and he maps for a beautiful run in transit. Right on the cusp of a maiden win and today could be his day. PROVE ME WRONG (5) is another who drops back in trip following a 3.9L defeat through the same race as CANTILEVER last time out. Needs a touch of luck from the draw, but she's racing well without winning and looks the main danger on her recent form. SHE'SATROOPER (7) was 1.9L away last start and the rise in trip is a big tick. Can go one better. DELTA LASS (11) not out of this with this looking a touch easier.
